<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>일정 목록</title>
    <style>
        .completed {
            color: gray;
            text-decoration: line-through;
        }
        .toolbar {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .schedule-item {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<h1>📅 일정 목록</h1>
<div class="toolbar">
    <a href="/schedules/new">➕ 새 일정 등록</a>
</div>
<hr>
<form method="get" action="/schedules">
    <input type="text" name="keyword" placeholder="제목 검색" value="{{keyword}}">
    <button type="submit">검색</button>
</form>
{{#scheduleList}}
    <div class="schedule-item {{#completed}}completed{{/completed}}">
        <h3>{{title}}</h3>
        <p>{{description}}</p>
        <p>마감일: {{dueDate}}</p>
        <p>완료 여부: {{#completed}}✅ 완료{{/completed}}{{^completed}}❌ 미완료{{/completed}}</p>

        <form action="/schedules/{{id}}/delete" method="post" style="display:inline;">
            <button type="submit">🗑 삭제</button>
        </form>
        <a href="/schedules/{{id}}/update">✏ 수정</a>
    </div>
{{/scheduleList}}



{{^scheduleList}}
    <p>등록된 일정이 없습니다.</p>
{{/scheduleList}}
</body>
</html>
